parameters: \knightThe way you channel magic... it's like nothing
I've ever seen before. However, you still are
not fully attuned to your powers. You have
yet to achieve your full potential.
\knightPerhaps it would be a good idea to
speak more with your goddess, Trailia.
\p3That's true... she's just hard to reach.
Can you please send her my regards?
\knightWill do. I'm sure that you'll know when she is
ready to speak with you. Just give it time.
\knightWith her power on your side, defeating \c[18]Apocalypse\c[0] will be a great deal easier!
\knightBest of luck to you four. Your work here is
done... but the rest of the Overworld still
needs saving. You're their only hope.
